  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">of one part to another, to which corresponds the order of one private individual to another. This order is directed by commutative justice , which is concerned about the mutual dealings between two persons . On the second place there is the order of the whole towards the parts, to which correspond</data>
