  <data key="d16">strong_textual_inference</data>
  <data key="d17">Injustice is twofold. First there is illegal injustice which is opposed to legal justice : and this is essentially a special vice , in so far as it regards a special object, namely the common good which it contemns; and yet it is a general vice , a</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_doctrinal</data>
</edge>
<edge source="concept.judge_role" target="concept.justice" id="edge.concept.judge_role.directed_to.concept.justice">
