  <data key="d16">strong_textual_inference</data>
  <data key="d17">far as it is an act of justice . Now it follows from what has been stated above ( Article 1, Replies to 1 and 3 ) that three conditions are requisite for a judgment to be an act of justice : first, that it proceed from the inclination of justice ; secondly, that it come from one who is in autho</data>
