  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q057.a001.obj1</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that right is not the object of justice . For the jurist Celsus says [Digest. i, 1; De Just. et Jure 1 that "right is the art of goodness and equality." Now art is not the object of justice , but is by itse</data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
<edge source="st.ii-ii.q057" target="st.ii-ii.q057.a002" id="structural.st.ii-ii.q057.contains.st.ii-ii.q057.a002">
  <data key="d6">structural.st.ii-ii.q057.contains.st.ii-ii.q057.a002</data>
