  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q063.a002.obj1</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that respect of persons does not take place in the dispensation of spiritual goods. For it would seem to savor of respect of persons if a man confers ecclesiastical dignity or benefice on account of consang</data>
