  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem lawful for clerics to kill evil -doers. For clerics especially should fulfil the precept of the Apostle ( 1 Corinthians 4:16 ): "Be ye followers of me as I also am of Christ ," whereby we are called upon to</data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
