  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q064.a005.obj1</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem lawful for a man to kill himself. For murder is a sin in so far as it is contrary to justice . But no man can do an injustice to himself, as is proved in Ethic. v, 11. Therefore no man sins by killing himse</data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
