  <data key="d17">As stated above ( Article 1 ), it is lawful to kill dumb animals, in so far as they are naturally directed to man's use, as the imperfect is directed to the perfect. Now every part is directed to the whole, as imperfect to perfect, wherefore every part is natu</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_structural_editorial</data>
