  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">In the goods three things may be considered in due order. First, the substantial integrity of the body, and this is injured by death or maiming. Secondly, pleasure or rest of the senses, and to this striking or anything causing a sense of pain is opposed. Thirdl</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_structural_editorial</data>
