  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">It is one thing to withhold the truth , and another to utter a falsehood. The former is lawful sometimes, for a man is not bound to divulge all truth , but only such as the judge can and must require of him according to the order of justice ; as, for instance,</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_structural_editorial</data>
