  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">To take usury for money lent is unjust in itself, because this is to sell what does not exist , and this evidently leads to inequality which is contrary to justice . In order to make this evident, we must observe that there are certain things the use of which</data>
